GOAL: How does frame get to the right computer

Repeater: A Hub. Takes signal from one of a port and then recreate multiple copies of frame and sent copied frame and then sent it out to all other connected cable

Using PowerShell: Physical address = MAC address

Address is broken into two halves: OEM and Unique ID

Every Network card needs a unique MAC address.

Part of EF is a CRC (Cyclic Redundancy Check): Verify if data is good and if not sent it back to hub
